# Project Structure

## Rules

- **File naming: kebab-case.** All files use kebab-case: `user-profile.tsx`, `auth.store.ts`, `date-utils.ts`. Never use PascalCase or camelCase for file names.
- **File suffixes indicate purpose.** Use `.store.ts` for Zustand stores, `.test.ts`/`.test.tsx` for tests, `.schema.ts` for Zod schemas, `.types.ts` for type-only files, `.constants.ts` for constants, `.utils.ts` for utility functions.
- **Import ordering** must follow this sequence, separated by blank lines:
  1. External packages (`react`, `zustand`, `@tanstack/react-query`, etc.)
  2. Aliased internal imports (`@/shared/...`, `@/modules/...`)
  3. Relative imports (`./`, `../`)
- **Maximum 1 level up for relative imports.** Never use `../../` or deeper. If you need to go more than one level up, use the `@/` alias instead.
- **Folder structure by module.** Feature code lives in `src/modules/<module-name>/`. Shared code lives in `src/shared/`.
- **Module folder structure:**
  - `src/modules/<module>/components/` - React components
  - `src/modules/<module>/hooks/` - Custom hooks
  - `src/modules/<module>/stores/` - Zustand stores
  - `src/modules/<module>/types/` - TypeScript types
  - `src/modules/<module>/utils/` - Utility functions
  - `src/modules/<module>/schemas/` - Zod schemas
  - `src/modules/<module>/constants/` - Constants
- **Shared folder structure:**
  - `src/shared/components/ui/` - Design system components (shadcn)
  - `src/shared/components/` - Shared non-UI components (layouts, error boundaries)
  - `src/shared/hooks/` - Shared hooks
  - `src/shared/utils/` - Shared utilities
  - `src/shared/types/` - Shared types
- **Index files for public API.** Each module should have an `index.ts` that re-exports its public API. Internal files should not be imported directly from outside the module.
- **Co-locate tests.** Place test files next to the file they test: `user-profile.tsx` and `user-profile.test.tsx` in the same directory.

## Examples

### Good

```typescript
// Correct import ordering
import { useState } from 'react';
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { z } from 'zod';

import { Button } from '@/shared/components/ui/button';
import { useAuthStore } from '@/modules/auth/stores/auth.store';
import { captureAppError } from '@/modules/sentry';

import { UserCard } from './user-card';
import { formatUserName } from '../utils/format-user';
```

```
// Correct file structure
src/
  modules/
    auth/
      components/
        login-form.tsx
        login-form.test.tsx
      hooks/
        use-auth.ts
      stores/
        auth.store.ts
      types/
        auth.types.ts
      schemas/
        login.schema.ts
      index.ts
    dashboard/
      components/
        dashboard-page.tsx
        stats-card.tsx
      index.ts
  shared/
    components/
      ui/
        button.tsx
        input.tsx
      layouts/
        app-layout.tsx
    hooks/
      use-debounce.ts
    utils/
      errors.ts
      datetime-utils.ts
    types/
      common.types.ts
```

### Bad

```typescript
// Wrong import ordering (mixed external and internal)
import { Button } from '@/shared/components/ui/button';
import { useState } from 'react';
import { UserCard } from './user-card';
import { z } from 'zod';

// Too many levels of relative imports
import { something } from '../../../shared/utils/helpers';
import { another } from '../../../../modules/auth/types';

// Wrong file naming
UserProfile.tsx        // PascalCase - wrong
userProfile.tsx        // camelCase - wrong
user_profile.tsx       // snake_case - wrong
```
